1
00:00:00,083 --> 00:00:01,375
My name is Younes

2
00:00:02,333 --> 00:00:04,208
I was born in 1969

3
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:08,458
I work as a driver

4
00:00:09,375 --> 00:00:13,458
My living conditions are average

5
00:00:15,416 --> 00:00:18,333
My education only goes up
to sixth grade in primary school

6
00:00:28,125 --> 00:00:32,083
Interviewer: In what year and how
were you detained in this prison?

7
00:00:32,208 --> 00:00:36,250
And what was the charge
you were detained for?

8
00:00:37,333 --> 00:00:39,375
In July 2016

9
00:00:42,083 --> 00:00:47,083
I was detained because I’d driven a woman alone in the car,
without a <i>mahram</i> [male guardian]

10
00:00:47,833 --> 00:00:51,125
They took my
personal papers, my ID

11
00:00:51,875 --> 00:00:55,500
I came to get the ID,
so they detained me

12
00:00:57,750 --> 00:01:00,833
I was detained for one day, then I
was whipped 100 lashes and released

13
00:01:01,583 --> 00:01:03,125
I mean, I got my ID
